Sentencas: The use of Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 (LSGM), a highly conducting oxygen ion electrolyte, in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC) technology requires suitable electrode materials.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: Because the Sr-doped LaMnO3 (LSM) cathode coupled with the YSZ electrolyte had shown relatively good performances, it has been also suggested for LSGM-based cells.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: As cathode overpotential is the main performance limitation, the optimization of the LSM/LSGM interface might be of fundamental relevance in the technology development of LSGM-based IT-SOFC.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: LSM films with different porosities were screen printed on both faces of the LSGM pellets; their morphology and electrical properties were investigated by scanning electron microscopy and impedance spectroscopy, respectively.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: Porosity was induced by the addition of icing sugar (3-5 wt%) to the LSM powder during ink preparation.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: Homogeneous electrode layers with a thickness of about 30 mu m were obtained.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: The higher the sugar amount, the higher the film porosity and the lower the LSM grain size.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: The Nyquist plots show two low frequency arcs to which the charge transfer and mass transfer process or oxygen dissociation process were associated, respectively.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte

Sentencas: One can expect that the best electrochemical performances are obtained using highly porous electrode.
Titulo: Impedance investigation on porous Sr-doped LaMnO3 films onto Sr-Mg-doped LaGaO3 electrolyte
